description: Meteor Garden is a 2001 Taiwanese drama starring Barbie Hsu with the members of Taiwanese boy band F4 (Jerry Yan, Vic Chou, Ken Chu and Vanness Wu). It is the first live-action television adaptation of the Japanese manga series Hana Yori Dango (Boys Over Flowers) by Kamio Yoko.
